---
title: Hidden Veggie, Mushroom & Lentil Lasagne with Mixed Leaf Salad & Parmesan
description: Construction is key when making a good lasagne but maybe more importantly is what you pack in it. Lay a sheet of lasagne and begin adding the rich tomato sauce dotted with hidden sautéed veggies and lovely mushrooms. Then another lasagne sheet and more sauce and more and more! Don’t forget the Parmesan to give it an extra zap.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
